data.description:
Discover the epitome of charm and convenience in this adorable townhouse nestled in the heart of Bartram. Welcome to Sumerlin at Bartram, a gated community that ensures both security and tranquility. This centrally located gem offers swift access to restaurants, shops, Baptist South hospital, and I95, making every convenience just moments away.

Step into a thoughtfully designed interior featuring 2 bedrooms and 2.5 full baths, accompanied by a versatile loft/flex space upstairs with built in-desk and cabinetry. The main floor boasts a seamless flow with a separate dining area, a well-appointed kitchen, and a cozy family room. Perfect for relaxation, the screened-in patio beckons for moments of serenity.

Parking is a breeze with 2 assigned spots directly out your front door. The HVAC was thoughtfully replaced in 2022 and the roof was replaced in 2018. 

Immerse yourself in the comfort and style of this townhouse, where modern living meets timeless charm.
